    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It has been my pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've kept it pampered in the garage, so the paint is sparkling and the interior is spotless. It's in truly flawless condition and ready for a new home. I'm so excited for whoever gets to drive this next\u2014you're going to love it! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
