    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one, preserving its factory-fresh appearance. The exterior boasts a mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, while the interior retains that signature new-car scent. Every stitch in the premium leather upholstery is perfect, and the dashboard remains untouched by UV rays. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; a full, documented service history accompanies the vehicle, showing proactive maintenance far exceeding factory recommendations. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, this is quite simply the finest example on the market today. It drives exactly as it did the moment it left the showroom floor\u2014tight, responsive, and powerful.",
      "price": 48900.0,
